# PI Planning System - Quick Start

> **Deterministic planning system with zero hallucination**

## What This Is

A complete workflow for planning development work using:

- **YAML** as single source of truth
- **Copilot Agents** for research & planning (controlled)
- **CLI tools** for validation & GitHub publishing
- **Zero hallucination** - LLMs only generate `.md` files, not issues

## TL;DR

```bash
# 1. Validate your plan
pnpm pi:validate

# 2. Generate planning docs
pnpm pi:plan

# 3. Create artifact templates
pnpm pi:artifacts

# 4. Use Copilot agents to fill templates
@workspace Using task-researcher.agent.md, research task T1
@workspace Using task-planner.agent.md, plan task T1

# 5. Review & approve (human gate)
# Check .copilot-tracking/ files

# 6. Publish to GitHub
export GITHUB_TOKEN="ghp_..."
pnpm pi:publish
```

