## Quick Example

### 1. Define a task in `planning/pi.yaml`:

```yaml
tasks:
    - key: T1
      title: "TASK: Implement book CRUD service"
      area: library
      priority: p0
      effort: 3
      dependsOn: []
      qa:
          unit: required
          integration: required
          coverage:
              statements: 95
              branches: 90
```

### 2. Generate & fill artifacts:

```bash
pnpm pi:artifacts  # Creates templates
```

Then use Copilot to research and plan:

```
@workspace Research T1 and fill .copilot-tracking/research/...
@workspace Plan T1 based on research
```

### 3. Publish to GitHub:

```bash
export GITHUB_TOKEN="ghp_your_token"
pnpm pi:publish
```

Creates:

- Epic issue (#123)
- Feature issue (#124, parent: #123)
- Task issue (#125, parent: #124)
- Sets Priority, Effort, Iteration in Project board

